I make myself available to you 24/7 until your project is complete, and you are totally happy with the result.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vcex_heading text="RELEVANT" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold"][vcex_spacing size="20px"][vc_column_text]Every creation is fully responsive and designed to fit your individual needs. I creatively incorporate the modules you need into your design.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" column_spacing="50" el_id="about" css=".vc_custom_1489870777691{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 15px !important;background-color: #eeeeee !important;}"][vc_column width="1/3"][vcex_image image_id="10"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vcex_heading text="ABOUT ME" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold"][vcex_spacing size="20px"][vc_column_text]Web design is my passion. Whether I'm creating an e-commerce website for a brick and mortar store, designing a new interface for a learning management system, or re-branding a well established company I always dedicate myself 100% to my project.[/vc_column_text][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_icon_box heading="Web Design" hover_white_text="" icon="globe" heading_type="h2" heading_transform="uppercase"]I'll develop the website you've always wanted for your business.[/vcex_icon_box][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_icon_box heading="REBRANDING" hover_white_text="" icon="rocket" heading_type="h2" heading_transform="uppercase"]Create a brand that lasts, with my expert help.[/vcex_icon_box][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_icon_box heading="TARGETED MARKETING" hover_white_text="" icon="smile-o" heading_type="h2" heading_transform="uppercase"]Get more customers with my optimization techniques.[/vcex_icon_box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row column_spacing="50" css=".vc_custom_1489870791428{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][vcex_heading text="SKILLS" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold"][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vc_column_text]No matter what project I'm working on, my solid skill set makes me capable of producing high quality work time after time. I'm very capable with Photoshop, HTML, CSS, PHP and MySQL. I'm also constantly attending conferences, camps, seminars and more to re-educate myself with current trends and tools.

I'd really love to work on your next project. Send me a note and let's see if we can't work something out. I just might be the perfect designer/developer for your project.[/vc_column_text][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_button url="#contact" target="local" title="Contact Me" style="outline" align="left" How I got here is a very long story, but my resume sums it up nicely.
You can see my accomplishments listed below, or download a copy to print.[/vc_column_text][vcex_spacing][vcex_button url="https://total.wpexplorer.com/graphix/wp-content/uploads/sites/27/2016/02/resume.pdf" target="blank" title="Download" style="outline" align="center" font_weight="bold" font_family="Lato" font_size="13px" letter_spacing="1.5px" font_padding="10px 20px" text_source="custom_text"]DOWNLOAD[/vcex_button][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row column_spacing="50" css=".vc_custom_1489870894758{margin-top: 50px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][vcex_heading text="EDUCATION" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold"][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vc_column_text]We all start somewhere, and for me that was school. icon_size="14px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row column_spacing="50" css=".vc_custom_1489870929353{padding-bottom: 15px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/2"][vcex_heading text="EXPERIENCE" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold"][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vc_column_text]Where you work and what you do can say a lot about you, and since I now work for myself I certainly have a lot to say.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vcex_spacing size="55px" visibility="hidden-phone"][vcex_heading text="WEB DESIGN & DEVELOPMENT SPECIALIST" link_local_scroll="" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold" font_size="16px"][vc_column_text]Websites-R-Us LLC, 2006-2010[/vc_column_text][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_heading text="WEB DESIGN INTERN" css=".vc_custom_1489870960703{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 15px !important;background-color: #eeeeee !important;}"][vc_column][vcex_heading text="MY WORK" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" font_weight="bold" text_align="center" font_size="26PX"][vcex_spacing size="20px"][vc_column_text font_size="16px"]

These examples are just a little bit of what I can do.
If you want to see more, just send me an email for my full portfolio.[/vc_column_text][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_image_grid columns="3" lightbox_title="false" lightbox_caption="false" columns_gap="25" img_hover_style="fade-in" img_rendering="" img_width="400" img_height="300" image_ids="21,22,23,24,25,26,27,28,29"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" typography_style="none" bg_style="stretch" style="light" el_id="contact" css=".vc_custom_1489870970377{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 15px !important;background-color: #222222 !important;}"][vc_column][vcex_heading text="CONTACT" link_local_scroll="" tag="h2" text_align="center" color="#ffffff" font_size="26px"][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vc_column_text color="#999999" font_size="16px"]

I'm always looking forward to my next adventure.
Send me a note, and let's get started on your project today![/vc_column_text][vcex_spacing size="25px"][vcex_form_shortcode style="white" full_width="true"][contact-form-7 id="34" title="Homepage"][/vcex_form_shortcode][/vc_column][/vc_row]
